# Spam Detection System 📩

## Overview

This project is a Machine Learning based Spam Detection System developed using Python, Streamlit, and Scikit-learn. It classifies text messages as Spam or Not Spam.

## Features

* Detects spam messages instantly
* User-friendly colorful interface
* Machine Learning based prediction
* Real-time message classification

## Technologies Used

* Python
* Pandas
* Scikit-learn
* Streamlit

## Dataset

The project uses an SMS spam dataset with:

* `v1` → Label (spam/ham)
* `v2` → Message text

## Installation

Install required packages:

pip install pandas scikit-learn streamlit

## Run Project

Run the application using:

py -m streamlit run SpamDetection.py

## Sample Inputs

Spam:
Congratulations! You won ₹50,000

Not Spam:
Hi, shall we meet tomorrow?

